# ============================================================================
# Notes
# ============================================================================
# This .gitignore follows GitHub's recommended patterns for:
# - .NET 8 Web API (C# / ASP.NET Core)
# - Next.js (JavaScript / TypeScript)
# - Node.js tooling
#
# Never commit:
# - Compiled binaries (.dll, .exe, .o)
# - Build artifacts (bin/, obj/, node_modules/, .next/)
# - Environment secrets (.env, appsettings.Development.json)
# - IDE user settings (.vs/, .idea/)
# - Database files (*.db, *.sqlite)
# - OS artifacts (.DS_Store, Thumbs.db)
#
# Safe to commit:
# - Source code (.cs, .ts, .tsx, .js)
# - Configuration templates (appsettings.json, .env.example)
# - Documentation (*.md)
# - Git config (.gitignore, .github/)
# - Project files (*.csproj, package.json)
